==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Knee jerk
<hw>Knee jerk</hw>. <fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>A jerk or forward kick of
the lower part of the leg produced by a blow or sudden strain upon the
patellar tendon of the knee, which causes a sudden contraction of the
quadriceps muscle; the patellar reflex.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Knee jerk</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Knee jerk
<hw>Knee jerk</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>emotional and predictable; -- of
certain people and their reactions to events.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Knee jerk liberal</ent>⟦br⟧
